Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:46.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bell Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:53.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:12.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone! We’re slipping off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:18.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,They blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two have been acting strangely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was totally Limone’s fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:54.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,They let her join us because she was supposed to be a great prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:16.50,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}White Solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:28.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had hoped that Chor Tempest would have recovered by now, but they haven’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’ve seen what Chor Tempest is like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:37.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were the only survivor from Chor Dextra. I’d like to hear your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:42.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,The situation certainly doesn’t look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:47.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can see that they’re a far cry from the elite choir that they once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:51.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,In their current state, they can barely handle daytime shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t look like we’ll be able to return them to night duty for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need them back at full strength right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:04:00.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s why we called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:03.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you do it, Sibylla Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run checks on the helical motors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,And don’t forget to clean the Simoun gems as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:18.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! Limone, what were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t screw Aaeru up like that! If you’re not going to do it right, you should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I… was told that I had to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:37.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re new, aren’t you? Are you… Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:45.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re Limone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:03.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Limone, your talent as a cadet was second to none.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:07.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,At the Academy, you broke most of the records for someone your age
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:13.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,both in written and practical tests, and you became the highest-ranked sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Central Command recognized your abilities and made a special exception for you:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:21.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,you were accepted as the youngest Sibylla in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,and assigned to Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you have zero experience in real combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,A few days ago, you went out on an unauthorized flight. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I’ve taken an interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:42.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Needless to say, you have an outstanding record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way Chor Tempest has ended up… doesn’t it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:52.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll bet you never thought being a Sibylla would be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:55.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It won’t be anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:05.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is listen to what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you do, you can go back to how things used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can reclaim the heights that a prodigy like you deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:20.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura seems to be using Limone to try to revive Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, well… taking care of the choirs is your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s just say…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:36.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,What those kids think is far beyond any adult’s understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:40.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re talking about trying to understand the youngest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:44.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously telling me that you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, let me tell you one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:54.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we’re doing out here… it’s war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:58.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even those kids understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:03.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who’s there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is a surprise! I didn’t expect you to come visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:46.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we were to break up as a pair, how would that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Comment: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:52.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that’s what you want, it’s fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:55.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don’t really…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was that all you wanted to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I cut his hands off the controls…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s nothing else we can do, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, go wait over there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:24.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Coming here wasn’t because of any decision I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was just doing what other people told me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:31.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,and before I knew it, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that you could tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,What would you do if you were told to kill somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, I don’t really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:45.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m not going to tell you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m here because I’m trying to {\i1}avoid{\i0} making a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:54.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you’re afraid of fighting, it’s okay to quit being a Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:58.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you’re not going to keep flying the Simoun, they aren’t going to let you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:07.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you really don’t have a reason to stay here, you can always leave, can’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, you are so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:37.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you’re going to be a splendid Simoun Sibylla someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, you need to be more considerate toward your teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:47.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,There isn’t anyone who can follow you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t butt in just because you can fly a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:15.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, why don’t you fly the Simoun any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s just that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, right now, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:32.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, what in the world are we supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:40.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that you know what to do. Please, you must tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:50.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now… I don’t have any strength to offer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:55.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all this time, I haven’t changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,A reconnaissance mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:20.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,There have been reports of possible large-scale military activities in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The north? From the Plumbum Highlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:27.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re more interested in how well Limone and Dominura are suited for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti and Floe are going with them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:35.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did they become a pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve heard that Dominura decided that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind of woman is she, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:46.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, Limone!
Comment: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:47.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,You go over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? The auriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:56.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:58.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,This seat should be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:12:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know all about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:06.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you know, then why…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I said, it’s for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ever since that incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,you have been unconsciously suppressing your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to set it free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn’t I tell you that I know you better than anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,She had Limone fly as her auriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks like she’s up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,How is it? Are you getting a feel for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ll be over the target soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:25.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep the communicator attached, and start the patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Limone, tell me something…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:45.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you really handle being an auriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or are you just doing as you’re told again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cut the chatter, please, and focus on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,And don’t ever ask Limone a question like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,It must be getting pretty cold out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,All clear to starboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,All clear dead ahead, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:49.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enemy tanks! Three o’clock low!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, there are a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re going in, too, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Doing the Silver Ri Maajon all of a sudden is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:45.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s impossible! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:52.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is she still holding on to what happened to her as a cadet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,This snow is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:46.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re late. Shouldn’t they be back by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh! There are just too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,This situation is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:09.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,In this blizzard, we can barely even fly, let alone do a Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:15.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the two of us are having this much trouble, then that brand new pair…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, we have to withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can’t do anything if we can’t draw a Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:24.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is a reconnaissance mission! We have to warn the others about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:39.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:54.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re late, so we came to fetch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:55.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re withdrawing immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:09.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, listen to what I’m telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,You need to figure it out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you just doing what you’re told again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silver Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, let’s do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger that. We’ll take them all out at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:51.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s suicide! Hardly anyone can do that Ri Maajon, and in these conditions…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silver Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s impossible! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s right! What I’ve wanted to do all along…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,is to make the most perfect Ri Maajons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,She did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of the enemy tanks are destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:17.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s as I thought: that girl really is a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:21.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I wasn’t wrong, after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.63,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:11.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m Kaimu, and I’m Sibylla Paraietta’s—Para-sama’s—pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:16.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:17.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wounds and Pain
